title: The provisions of sub Regulation no 1(b) of this Regulation shall not be applicable where the share of MHADA and MCGM land has already been handed over as per then prevailing Regulations
clause_text: The provisions of sub Regulation no 1(b) of this Regulation shall not be applicable where the share of MHADA and MCGM land has already been handed over as per then prevailing Regulations. ( Clause 11 kept in abeyance)
